1. 3 tier arch.
     -presentation layer
          *UI
          *JSP
                >decouple layers(single method connection between layers)
      -business layer 
         *business logic

       -data layer
            *code for managing database.(DBMANAGER)


2. mvc
  -Controller
    (911 disbatch)
      -decide where to pass info
      
  -model
    handles data from controller
    
  -view
    sends response to user.
    
    
    
